ESG and Sustainability Trends Influencing Industry Strategies
Environmental, Social, and Governance (ESG) considerations are increasingly shaping corporate strategies within the VSSNS landscape. Platforms are under mounting pressure from regulators, investors, and consumers to demonstrate sustainable practices, transparency, and social responsibility. This shift manifests in multiple dimensions:

Content Moderation and Digital Well-being: Companies are investing in AI-driven moderation tools to combat misinformation, hate speech, and harmful content, aligning with social responsibility mandates.
Carbon Neutrality Initiatives: Major platforms are committing to carbon reduction goals by optimizing data center operations, utilizing renewable energy sources, and promoting eco-friendly content creation practices.
